{"id":567422,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/09/【麻辣总局】终于把人民扔到一边/","date":"2017-09-05T07:05:39Z","modified":"2017-09-05T07:05:39Z","title":"【麻辣总局】终于把人民扔到一边","content":"<p>近日，有网友发现，曾被列入小学生教材的《上学歌》，在出现于最新教育部版小学一年级上册的时候，内容发生了改动：将曾经的“长大要为人民立功劳”改为了“长大要为祖国立功劳”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/image_uploaded_from_ios_720.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-567424\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/image_uploaded_from_ios_720.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"606\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/image_uploaded_from_ios_720.jpg 534w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/image_uploaded_from_ios_720-223x300.jpg 223w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">以下为早期版本</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/image_uploaded_from_ios_720-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-567423\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/image_uploaded_from_ios_720-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/image_uploaded_from_ios_720-1.jpg 405w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/image_uploaded_from_ios_720-1-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,13789],"tags":[33259,14732,10435,22021,15859]}